methods.name: void resize(int startIndex, int elements)
methods.comment:
* Resizes the buffers for VM to fill in the next batch of stack frames. * The next batch will start at the given startIndex with the maximum number * of elements. * *

Subclass may override this method to manage the allocated buffers. * * @param startIndex the start index for the first frame of the next batch to fill in. * @param elements the number of elements for the next batch to fill in. *
